vote.title: Authorize (1) the adoption of a Resolution of Support for Sycamore Strategies, LLC, and/or its affiliate(s) (Applicant), related to its application to the Texas Department of Housing and Community Affairs for 9% Low Income Housing Tax Credits for the development Cabana Design District Apartment Homes to be located at 899 North Stemmons Freeway, Dallas, Texas 75207; and (2) an agreement with the Applicant for a line of credit in the amount of $500.00 for the proposed multifamily development - Not to exceed $500.00 - Financing: General Fund
